d 'XTCSDQ': module to implement Tests of no cross-sectional error dependence in panel quantile regressions
d
d      xtcsdq tests whether the residuals of a panel quantile
d regression exhibit cross-sectional	dependence (CSD), based on
d Demetrescu, Hosseinkouchack & Rodrigues (2023).    This is a
d residual-based diagnostic test.  It examines pairwise
d correlations among the quantile    regression errors after
d fitting a QR model. The variables you supply define the model   
d specification — they are not tested directly. 
d
d KW: panel data
d KW: quantile regression
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260307
d
d Author:   Merwan Roudane, NA
d Support: email  merwanroudane920@@gmail.com
d
f xtcsdq.ado
f xtcsdq.sthlp
